Text:
Support is necessary to place floating crystals above Z-level 1.  
Self-stackable  
Will be invisible and have no hitbox when playing.
Floats in the sky to support a sky island.
"How does it work?" Oh? Oh, now? After all these years? After all these games? Now you ask ME how those work?

Visually deletes the ground beneath it.  
Acts as a negative water source to remove water falling off the islands.  
The flag will not be visible in-game.
Visually removes the ground beneath it. For locations where you would never expect to see water.
A place for beavers to meet and chat over a cup of freshly squeezed lemonade, and to teach little kits about capitalism.
"When life gives you lemons… please don't burn someone’s house down with them."
